title: Grateful Dead Live at UIC Pavilion on 1987-04-10
description:
Set I
Shakedown Street, Little Red Rooster, Candyman, Me & My Uncle > Mexicali Blues, Brown Eyed Women, Cassidy > Don't Ease Me In
Set II
Iko Iko > Looks Like Rain, Box Of Rain > He's Gone > Drums > Space > The Other One > Black Peter > Around & Around > Turn On Your Lovelight

Encore:
It's All Over Now Baby Blue


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
